text: Gianelli is a surname. Notable people with the surname include: *Carlos Gianelli (born 1948), Uruguayan lawyer and diplomat *John Gianelli (born 1950), American basketball player *William Gianelli (born 1919), United States Army personnel ==See also== *21588 Gianelli, main-belt asteroid *Gianelli Power Plant, power plant in California.
